## 11. Components Used

### Cutting System

* TCT Saw Blade

  * Diameter: 255 mm
  * Teeth: 80
  * High wear resistance
  * Low vibration

### Motor

* BLDC Motor (CY-1518)

  * Voltage: 48V
  * Power: 1500W
  * Speed: 3000–5000 RPM

